#. module: account_tax_fixed_amount_multiplier
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account_tax_fixed_amount_multiplier.field_account_tax__fixed_amount_multiplier
msgid ""
"Controls how the quantity is used for fixed-amount taxes:\n"
"- No Multiplier: the amount is applied once per line.\n"
"- Quantity (default): multiplied by the line quantity, regardless of the unit of measure.\n"
"- Product Quantity: the line quantity is converted to the product's unit of measure before multiplying.\n"
"- Product Weight: multiplied by the total weight (product quantity × product weight)."
msgstr ""

